1. mkdir ~/bin

2. mv commit_animation ~/bin

3. chmod u+x ~/bin/commit_animation

4. mv pre-commit .git/hooks/

5. chmod u+x .git/hooks/pre-commit

*****

my Hook file is in .git/hooks/pre-commit.
This file on commit finds *.cpp files, and checks whether "p r i n t ()" statemant exist in them.
In that case error message is p r i n t ed and commmit is aborted)